idioms \- overview of idiomatic utilities for scripting
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
\fBidioms\fP is a set of useful utilities designed to make scripting more idiomatic, and make shell
usage perhaps so too. It\(cqs akin to \f(CRmoreutils\fP, but the main goal is to standardize common tasks,
improve code quality and quality of life.
